{"tid":2367511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鎮壓蒙古語運動後 內蒙古停用中小學歷史文化教科書","createTime":"2021-01-15T11:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T12:23:10.000Z","uid":63183,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca5ab563651ab17bbea9f4021137911c896de01","tid":2367511,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"出處：港語學<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/4930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F4930&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=d974a0f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/4930</a><br />\n<br />\n喺上年9月開學嘅時候，因為內蒙古實施漢語取締蒙古語嘅教育政策，引來蒙古人大規模罷課同公民抗命運動，但最終政府並冇聽蒙古人嘅訴求，反而用搵軍警鎮壓、宵禁同埋通緝參與嘅學生。今個新學期，內蒙古政府將運動成因歸究喺中小學歷史教科書問題，宣布將一批「強調個體民族身分」嘅歷史教科書停用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/photo_2021-01-15_12-48-44.jpg?w=678&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fphoto_2021-01-15_12-48-44.jpg%3Fw%3D678%26ssl%3D1&h=d5334e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內蒙古自治區教育廳喺1月8號公布「關於停止使用《內蒙古歷史與文化》等自治區中小學地方課程教材的函」，話喺上年9月秋季國家教材委員會對地方課程做咗意識形態審查，指責呢啲歷史書歷史階段分期同全國統編教材不一，鑄牢中華民族共同體意識不夠突出，刻意強調個體的「民族身份」同「民族意識」」，闡述中華民族共同性不足。<br />\n<br />\n經審查後，教育廳決定由2021年春季學期起即時停用《內蒙古歷史與文化》、《蒙古族歷史》《河奪靈史與文化》等地方教材，由9月秋季課程起停用講述城市歷史嘅《呼倫貝爾歷史與文化》《科爾沁歷史與文化》。"},{"pid":"50324f9cca92290c2bacde86c30c79819570ab1f","tid":2367511,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"成吉思汗啲後代咁鬼渣"},{"pid":"ddd6d56ab5f1d8dd4baa971cb2d8cea74e4de6d9","tid":2367511,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e293edbd2d5cf132c8e5eeda0dda3094a4a4f219","tid":2367511,"uid":151544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"今日蒙古，今日香港"},{"pid":"0730d53371bea83182ca56526f470785be613eeb","tid":2367511,"uid":282569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"所有「自治區」、「特别行政區」都只係得個名<br />\n<br />\n乾脆變返矖做省、市算啦屌"},{"pid":"a4bda8809897418ead2a463427d0d8d93cef1175","tid":2367511,"uid":42982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0730d53371bea83182ca56526f470785be613eeb","tid":2367511,"uid":282569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"所有「自治區」、「特别行政區」都只係得個名<br />\n<br />\n乾脆變返矖做省、市算啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"特別高壓d"},{"pid":"18345c73b98709b2e9d49e7367068d489c3ea19f","tid":2367511,"uid":63183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mQL4aE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mQL4aE.png&h=fadba435&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}